      <p>These massive carnivores weigh more than 1,800 pounds and stand nearly 9 feet tall when they rear up on their hind legs. They are bad-tempered and territorial. The <a href="ch73s06.html#MonstersAnimals18">brown bear's</a> statistics can be used for almost any big bear, including the grizzly.</p>
