        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals19"/>
        <p>A <a href="ch73s06.html#MonstersAnimals18">brown bear</a> attacks mainly by tearing at opponents with its claws.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2273047"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals20"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Improved Grab (Ex):</strong></span> To use this ability, a <a href="ch73s06.html#MonstersAnimals18">brown bear</a> must hit with a claw attack. It can then attempt to start a grapple as a free action without provoking an attack of opportunity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
